Private/All ChatRoom Example
Almost the same as ChatRoomServer. Only some if/else added.
Conversations are store as txt file for each conversation client side.

    

Usage:
Before Start Server/client
Check line 21-21 in chatRoomClientRealtime.py and line 6-7 in ChatRoomServer.py same
1: Start Server(python ChatRoomServer.py)
2: Start client/clients(python chatRoomClientRealtime.py)
3: For send private message to another client enter  "targetname>message" in sender client console.
4:For see old messages with client or allchat enter "conversation>targetname or all" 
(Actions can be traceable in server console. Connections. messages ex.) 